<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" data-bs-theme="light">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/images/favicon.svg" type="image/x-icon">
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playpen+Sans:wght@100..800&family=Poppins:ital,wght@0,100;0,200;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;0,800;0,900;1,100;1,200;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,600;1,700;1,800;1,900&family=Shadows+Into+Light&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/all.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/bootstrap.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
    <title>MaMa's Spaghetti'</title>
</head>

<body data-bs-spy="scroll" data-bs-target="#navId">
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg text-black position-fixed w-100 z-2 bg1" id="navId">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand fw-bold text-uppercase" href="#"><img src="/images/logo.png" alt="logo"> MaMa's
                Spaghetti</a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                data-bs-target="#navbarSupportedContent" aria-controls="navbarSupportedContent" aria-expanded="false"
                aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarSupportedContent">
                <ul class="navbar-nav ms-md-auto mb-2 mb-lg-0 align-items-center">
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link active" aria-current="page" href="#home">Home</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="#about">About</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="#services">Services</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="#recipes">Recipes</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="#contact">Contact</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <% if (user) { %>
                            <a class="nav-link" href="profile"><img class="rounded-circle" src="<%=user.img%>" alt="user-img"></a>
                            <% } else { %>
                                <a class="nav-link" href="#sign">Sign Up</a>
                                <% } %>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-moon fa-lg" id="darkModeToggle"></i>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <section class="home vh-100" id="home" data-scroll-index="0">
        <div class="container h-100 d-flex flex-column align-items-center justify-content-center text-center">
            <h1 class="text-white mb-5">MaMa's Spaghetti</h1>
            <p class="fs-4 mb-0">Just Like MaMa Used to Make</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about bg1" id="about" data-scroll-index="1">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row g-4">
                <div class="col-xl-4">
                    <div class="inner ">
                        <img src="/images/Family Baking Time.jpeg" alt="about-img" class="w-100 rounded-3">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xl-8">
                    <div class="inner">
                        <h2 class="fs-1">About Us</h2>
                        <p>At MaMa’s Spaghetti, we believe that the best meals come straight from the heart — and from
                            MaMa’s kitchen. Our collection brings you comforting, home-cooked recipes just like the ones
                            Mom used to make: rich in flavor, made with love, and always satisfying. Whether you're
                            looking for a classic Sunday pasta, a cozy soup, or a nostalgic dessert, we've got you
                            covered. Every recipe is crafted to bring back those warm family moments and help you create
                            new ones around your own table.</p>
                        <p>Our mission is simple — to make cooking at home feel less like a chore and more like coming
                            home. You don’t need fancy ingredients or complicated steps here; just honest food, made the
                            way MaMa did. Whether you're a beginner in the kitchen or a seasoned home cook, our recipes
                            are designed to be approachable, forgiving, and full of heart.</p>
                        <p>Food is more than nourishment — it’s a connection to our roots, our culture, and our
                            families. At MaMa’s Recipes, we aim to preserve those traditions and share them with the
                            world, one dish at a time. So grab a spoon, pour yourself some tea, and stay awhile. You're
                            always welcome at MaMa’s table.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="services bg2" id="services" data-scroll-index="2">
        <div class="top">
            <h2>Services</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="container d-flex flex-column flex-xl-row gap-4">
            <div class="search w-md-50 d-flex justify-content-center flex-column text-center">
                <h3>Search</h3>
                <p class="text-secondary">One of our website's standout features is the ability to search for recipes by
                    a specific dish name or individual ingredients. Whether you’re craving something particular or just
                    trying to use up what’s in your fridge, our smart search helps you discover delicious recipes that
                    match exactly what you have on hand</p>
                <button class="btn btn-outline-dark"><a href="recipes.ejs" class=" text-decoration-none">Search for a
                        Recipe</a></button>
            </div>
            <img src="/images/hero-img.png" alt="mid-service" class="mid-service">
            <div class="add w-md-50 d-flex justify-content-center flex-column text-center">
                <h3>Add</h3>
                <p class="text-secondary">Another great feature of our website is the ability to add your own recipes.
                    Whether it’s a cherished family dish or a creative new idea, you can easily share it with others.
                    Add ingredients, steps, and photos to build your recipe and inspire fellow food lovers in the
                    community. Just sign in with your account and share your favorite MaMa's Recipes</p>
                <button class="btn btn-outline-dark" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#staticBackdrop">Add a
                    Recipe</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <div class="modal fade service-modal" id="staticBackdrop" data-bs-backdrop="static" data-bs-keyboard="false"
        tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="staticBackdropLabel" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <div class="modal-header">
                    <h1 class="modal-title fs-5" id="staticBackdropLabel">New Recipe</h1>
                    <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <form id="recipeForm">
                        <div>
                            <label for="RecipeImg" class="col-form-label">Recipe's image :</label>
                            <input type="file" name="RecipeImg" id="RecipeImg" class="w-100 rounded-2 mt-2"
                                accept="image/*" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label for="RecipeName" class="col-form-label"></label>
                            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="RecipeName" name="RecipeName"
                                placeholder="Recipe for" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mb-3 d-flex">
                            <label for="Ingredients" class="col-form-label"></label>
                            <input type="text" class="form-control me-2" id="Ingredients" name="Ingredients"
                                placeholder="Ingredients">
                            <button class="btn btn-outline-dark" id="addIngBtn" disabled>+</button>
                        </div>
                        <div class="ings mb-3 d-flex flex-wrap" id="ings">

                        </div>
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label for="RecipeDescription" class="col-form-label"></label>
                            <textarea class="form-control" id="RecipeDescription" placeholder="Description"
                                name="RecipeDescription" required></textarea>
                        </div>
                        <div class="modal-footer">
                            <button type="button" class="btn btn-dark" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Cancel</button>
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-outline-dark" id="addRecBtn" data-bs-dismiss="modal"
                                disabled>Add Recipe</button>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="toast-container position-fixed bottom-0 end-0 p-3 recipe-toast">
        <div id="liveToast" class="toast" role="alert" aria-live="assertive" aria-atomic="true">
            <div class="toast-header">
                <strong class="me-auto">MaMa's Kitchen</strong>
                <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="toast" aria-label="Close"></button>
            </div>
            <div class="toast-body">
                Recipe Added Successfully
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <section class="sign_reminder text-center" id="sign" data-scroll-index="5">
        <% if (user) { %>
            <h3 class="fs-1">Welcome, <%= user.name %>!</h3>
            <a href="profile"><img class="rounded-circle border border-5 border-light" src="<%=user.img%>" alt="user-img"></a>
            <% } else { %>
                <h3 class="fs-1">Don't Have an Account yet!</h3>
                <a href="signLogin" class="btn btn-outline-dark">Sign-up</a>
                <% } %>
    </section>

    <section class="recipes bg1" id="recipes" data-scroll-index="3">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="top">
                <h2>Recipes</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="row g-4">
                <% for(var i=0;i<2;i++){ %>
                <div class="col-xl-4 col-md-6">
                    <div class="inner">
                        <div class="card shadow">
                            <div class="img-box overflow-hidden">
                                <img src="<%= recipes[i].img %>" alt="<%= recipes[i].title %>">
                            </div>
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <a href="recipes"
                                    class="text-black text-decoration-none d-flex justify-content-between">
                                    <h5 class="card-title"><%= recipes[i].title %></h5><span>View Recipe <i
                                            class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i></span>
                                </a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <% } %>
                <div class="col-xl-4 order-md-first order-xl-last">
                    <div class="inner">
                        <div class="card shadow">
                            <div class="img-box overflow-hidden">
                                <img src="/images/download.jpeg" alt="">
                            </div>
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <a href="recipes"
                                    class="text-black text-decoration-none d-flex justify-content-between">
                                    <h5 class="card-title">MaMa's Recipes</h5><span>View More Recipes <i
                                            class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i></span>
                                </a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="contact bg2" id="contact" data-scroll-index="4">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="top">
                <h2>Contact Us.</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="row g-4 text-center">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="inner d-flex flex-column gap-2 align-items-center justify-content-center">
                        <div class="icon d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center bg2">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-location-arrow fs-4"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h6 class="fw-bold">Address</h6>
                        <p class="text-secondary">6834 Hollywood Blvd - Los Angeles CA</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="inner d-flex flex-column gap-2 align-items-center justify-content-center">
                        <div class="icon d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center bg2">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-envelope fs-4"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h6 class="fw-bold">Email</h6>
                        <p class="text-secondary">Support@website.com</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="inner d-flex flex-column gap-2 align-items-center justify-content-center">
                        <div class="icon d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center bg2">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-phone fs-4"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h6 class="fw-bold">Phone</h6>
                        <p class="text-secondary">+20 012 4567 8910</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <form>
                <div class="row gx-4 text-center">
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <div class="inner">
                            <label for="Name" class="form-label"></label>
                            <input type="text" placeholder="Name" id="Name"
                                class="Name form-control-sm border-0 py-2 w-100" required>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <div class="inner">
                            <label for="email" class="form-label"></label>
                            <input type="text" placeholder="Email" id="email"
                                class="email form-control-sm border-0 py-2 w-100" required>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12 mb-3">
                        <div class="inner">
                            <label for="message" class="form-label"></label>
                            <textarea class="message form-control-sm border-0 py-2 w-100" id="message"
                                placeholder="Message" rows="7" required></textarea>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <button class="btn btn-outline-dark align-self-start px-5 py-2">Submit</button>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center text-secondary py-4 text-center bg-black">
            <p class="mb-0">Copy Right 2025 © By <span class="fw-bold"><a href="#"
                        class="text-decoration-none fs-5">MaMa's Spaghetti</a></span> All Rights Reserved</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="/js/darkMood.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/script.js"></script>
</body>

</html>